'''Grant Davies''' (born [[September 11]], [[1963]]) is a retired [[Australia|Australian]] professional [[canoeing|canoer]]. He competed in [[Canoeing at the 1988 Summer Olympics]] and won a [[silver medal]] in the K 1 1000 metres.

